u$ more concretely? Specifically, what is the support of $g$ ? What is the exact relation between $g$ and $\xi$ ? Specifically, is $\xi$ absolutely continuous w.r.t. $\eta$ ?  (I believe it isn't.) Bonus question: I am aware that the Fourier-Stieltjes transform $\hat\xi$ of $\xi$ is $u\mapsto e^{-2i\pi u} \prod_{j=1}^{\infty} \cos^2(2\pi u/3^j)$ (the square of that of $
